MASH Research Group
University of California, Berkeley
ns@mash.cs.berkeley.edu
<http://www-mash.cs.berkeley.edu/ns/>

VINT Project
A collaboration among USC/ISI, Xerox PARC, LBNL, and UCB 
<http://netweb.usc.edu/vint/>

This directory contains a source code or binary distribution of nam,
the UCB/LBNL Network AniMator. 
Nam is intended to be used with the UCB/LBNL Network Simulator, NS. 
Nam should configure with GNU autoconfigure.
Additional information:

QUICK START:  try
	./configure

DOWNLOADING AND BUILDING NAM:
	<http://www-mash.cs.berkeley.edu/ns/ns-build.html>

INSTALLATION PROBLEMS AND BUG FIXES:
	<http://www-mash.cs.berkeley.edu/nam/nam-problems.html>

DOCUMENTATION:
	<http://www-mash.cs.berkeley.edu/ns/>
	nam.1   (the nam man page, included in this distribution)

INFORMATION ABOUT NS:
	<http://www-mash.cs.berkeley.edu/ns/>

LATEST INFORMATION:
	<http://www-mash.cs.berkeley.edu/nam/>

